      landingDescription: 'In pursuit of our vision to achieve prosperity and a safe climate through sustainable energy, Energy Foundation China is dedicated to establishing a knowledge hub through publicly available information. This hub aims to provide policymakers, researchers, students, and other stakeholders with free and open access to reliable knowledge on energy and climate change topics. Our goal is to foster informed and impactful transition actions toward zero emissions.',
