      policy7Title: 'VII. How We Protect Your Personal Information',
      policy7Text1: 'We pay great attention to the security of your personal information. If the Platform collects any personal information, we will implement reasonable control and appropriate technical and organizational measures in accordance with national laws and regulations to protect personal information, and maintain the security of our information and systems related to personal information to prevent unauthorized access to, disclosure, use, modification, damage, or loss of data. Files containing personal information are protected to varying degrees according to the level of sensitivity of the information they contain. In addition, we apply appropriate control measures (such as access restriction) on the computer system and apply them as appropriate. We also take reasonable measures to ensure that only authorized employees can have access to personal information.',      
      policy8Title: 'VIII. Your Rights',
      policy8Text1: 'You can access and manage your personal information in the following ways when you use the Platform.',
      policy8_1Subtitle: '(I) Access and correct your personal information',
      policy8_1Text1: 'You can contact us with the contact information specified in Section XI below to access and correct your personal information.',
