      policy8_2List3: '3. Where we use and process your personal information in breach of the agreement with you;',
      policy8_2List4: '4. Where you no longer use our products or services;',
      policy8_2List5: '5. Where we cease to provide services to you.',
      policy8_2Text2: 'You may request the deletion of your personal information by contacting us with the contact information specified in Section XI of the Policy, and we will respond to your request within 15 working days. When we delete your personal information from servers, we may not immediately delete the same data from the backup system, but we will delete the information when the backup is updated.',
      policy8_2Text3: 'Please note that where the storage period as stipulated by laws and administrative regulations has not been reached, or where it is technically difficult to delete your personal information, we may not be able to delete your personal information, but will promptly stop processing your personal information.',      
      policy8_3Subtitle: '(III) Withdraw Your Consent',
      policy8_3Text1: 'Certain functions may require some basic personal information to be completed. You may give or withdraw at any time your consent to the collection and use of additional personal information. Your withdrawal of consent will not affect our previous processing of your personal information, but we will cease to process your personal information. You may change the authorized scope by contacting us with the contact information specified in Section XI below.',
      policy8_4Subtitle: '(IV) Access a copy of your personal information',
      policy8_4Text1: 'You may obtain a copy of your personal information by contacting us with the contact information specified in Section XI below. We may also transfer a copy of your personal information directly to a third party designated by you upon your request, provided that the relevant technology is feasible.',
      policy9Title: 'IX. How We Process Personal Information of Minors',
      policy9Text1: 'Our products, websites and services are primarily intended for adults. Minors under the age of 14 may not use our products or services without the consent of parents or guardians. For the personal information collected from minors with the consent of their parents, we will use or disclose the information only as permitted by laws, with the express consent of their parents or guardians, or as necessary for protecting minors.',
